summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from Henry Furhman and Carrie Furhman, his wife, of Seattle, Washington, to the City of Seattle, dated the 28th day of August, 1905 to Lots One (1), Two (2), Three (3), Four (4), Eleven (11), Twelve (12), Thirteen (13) and Fourteen (14) in Block Two (2) of Denny Furhman Addition to the City of Seattle.
